messages.msgSnippet: HI. I found this on another list and thought I would let yous know. Information for homeschoolers preparing for college:
messages.messageBody:
HI. I found this on another list and thought I would let yous know.

Information for homeschoolers preparing for college:
http://www.collegeboard.com/article/0,3868,5-25-0-56,00.html

Just in case doesn't work, go to collegeboard.com; click on parents; click on "Action Plan " (bottom right) , " Freshman" (bottom right)

then, click on " how to search for Volunteer Opportunities"
then, click on "For Gifted Students" (bottom right)
then, click on "Home-Schooled Students & Admission" (bottom right)


[Non-text portions of this message have been removed]
